ttps://holland.pk/vu01mlgf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvu01mlgf&h=354fa62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過單靠部機我覺得對床蝨冇乜用，可能仲係頭一星期，我係要配合埋滅蝨水，滅蝨粉一齊用，朝早夜晚對住床鳩噴，味道幾香佢話冇毒，半個鐘D味就散哂<br />\n<br />\n而家時間係早6：11，少左8成蝨都冇，死屍就有"},{"pid":"8059bfdc1986731d7a060d399723ce5109964b25","tid":361562,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T22:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mzhxjvg1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmzhxjvg1&h=87fbacef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死屍呀"},{"pid":"268020b8fcdb23c069ac6853c671080060374f30","tid":361562,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T22:15:21.000Z","msg":"但係有時仲會俾咬手，果D應該係睇唔到既蝨"},{"pid":"f1ec33c3be6d779f0d844b83891d840407786edd","tid":361562,"uid":100904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係有時仲會俾咬手，果D應該係睇唔到既蝨</blockquote><br />\n樓主原本木蝨個量有幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e211968f7591f3a45b611d1084b08fd0341ef19e","tid":361562,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"有冇多啲close up"},{"pid":"2783424347deb57471a34734ec53e46ff738d1cc","tid":361562,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"我屋企之前都有  張床褥一定唔要得，可以扔就扔咗佢 <br />\n 你個包粉我都有用 用完的確死咗大部分 係陣味有啲臭"},{"pid":"bb0d95ba8b6c91e22a19ec81975c8793e7108357","tid":361562,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係有時仲會俾咬手，果D應該係睇唔到既蝨</blockquote><br />\n樓主原本木蝨個量有幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c54f20a05c1cf0c3b182607b7ef69f0ab5bbac4","tid":361562,"uid":40194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite